nd 200 breaststroke finals on the same day), then capped it with a gold in the 200 IM.\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his legacy\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3405}, {\"ngram\": \"a historic double (golds\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3462}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 butterfly\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3483}, {\"ngram\": \"200 breaststroke finals\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3511}, {\"ngram\": \"the same day\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3527}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 IM\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a great showing overall for the host country, which finished fifth in golds (16) and fourth in total medals (64).\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great showing\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3595}, {\"ngram\": \"the host country\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3624}, {\"ngram\": \"golds\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3655}, {\"ngram\": \"total medals\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll remember Teddy Riner closing out his legendary Olympic judo career with golds in the individual and team competition, and the way the spirited fans added to the scene in a handful of other sports.\", \"from\": 3694, \"to\": 3897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3710, \"end\": 3721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teddy_Riner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teddy Riner\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teddy_Riner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teddy_Riner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his legendary Olympic judo career\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3767}, {\"ngram\": \"golds\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3778}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual and team competition\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3817}, {\"ngram\": \"the spirited fans\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3848}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3867}, {\"ngram\": \"a handful\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 3884, \"to\": 3896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was the final act of a dramatic three-part play that were Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Rio, Tokyo and Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 4002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3972, \"end\": 3975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.492991795684218e-42, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3977, \"end\": 3982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999735509849, \"rank\": 2.6448871881427927e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 3987, \"end\": 4001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final act\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3921}, {\"ngram\": \"a dramatic three-part play\", \"from\": 3925, \"to\": 3951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was already the absolute greatest ever in her sport, to the point that Olympic medals shouldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have really mattered much to her legacy.\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4058}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4072}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic medals\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4092}, {\"ngram\": \"her legacy\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after everything she dealt with in Tokyo\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the twisties, pulling ou