"to\": 5738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The race was settled by fivethousandthsof a second, as in three decimal places.\", \"from\": 5740, \"to\": 5819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The race\", \"from\": 5740, \"to\": 5748}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 5782, \"to\": 5790}, {\"ngram\": \"three decimal places\", \"from\": 5798, \"to\": 5818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcer totally botched the call, leading to a dramatic and confusing moment while everyone waited to see who won and then found out,Oh, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the super famous guy we spent months hearing about leading up to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5820, \"to\": 6048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The announcer\", \"from\": 5820, \"to\": 5833}, {\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 5850, \"to\": 5858}, {\"ngram\": \"a dramatic and confusing moment\", \"from\": 5871, \"to\": 5902}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5909, \"to\": 5917}, {\"ngram\": \"the super famous guy\", \"from\": 5970, \"to\": 5990}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6006}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6035, \"to\": 6047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then a few days later, he won a bronze medal in his better event, the 200 meters, and shortly after he crossed the finish linewe found out he was racing with COVID-19.\", \"from\": 6049, \"to\": 6220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6211, \"end\": 6219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.772882509902805e-14, \"text\": \"COVID-19\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 6083, \"to\": 6097}, {\"ngram\": \"his better event\", \"from\": 6101, \"to\": 6117}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish linewe\", \"from\": 6164, \"to\": 6181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, you wouldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have believed the script.\", \"from