\": 10654, \"to\": 10671}, {\"ngram\": \"celebrities\", \"from\": 10675, \"to\": 10686}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 10690, \"to\": 10700}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 10710, \"to\": 10716}, {\"ngram\": \"NBC\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s payroll\", \"from\": 10720, \"to\": 10735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea of having the surfing take place about 10,000 miles away from the Olympic Village was surprising enough that the thought of sending a comedian to cover it felt routine.\", \"from\": 10737, \"to\": 10914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10812, \"end\": 10827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3498752260953164e-40, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 10737, \"to\": 10745}, {\"ngram\": \"the surfing\", \"from\": 10756, \"to\": 10767}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 10773, \"to\": 10778}, {\"ngram\": \"the thought\", \"from\": 10855, \"to\": 10866}, {\"ngram\": \"a comedian\", \"from\": 10878, \"to\": 10888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that will be a quirky little thing that I predict will outlast the memory of who won a bunch of the 329 gold medals.\", \"from\": 10915, \"to\": 11035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a quirky little thing\", \"from\": 10932, \"to\": 10953}, {\"ngram\": \"the memory\", \"from\": 10982, \"to\": 10992}, {\"ngram\": \"a bunch\", \"from\": 11004, \"to\": 11011}, {\"ngram\": \"the 329 gold medals\", \"from\": 11015, \"to\": 11034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you measure Olympic moments by how loudly I yelled at my television when they happened, I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t think anything from Paris surpassed thewalk-off try from Alex \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSpiff\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Sedrick that gave the U.S. women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s rugby sevens team a bronze medal.\", \"from\": 11037, \"to\": 11282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11158, \"end\": 11163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7950847303899912e-31, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 11195, \"end\": 11199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.72626068272985e-11, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic moments\", \"from\": 11052, \"to\": 11067}, {\"ngram\": \"my television\", \"from\": 11094, \"to\": 11107}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 11144, \"to\": 11152}, {\"ngram\": \"thewalk-off try\", \"from\": 11174, \"to\": 11189}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 11230, \"to\": 11238}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby\", \"from\": 11249, \"to\": 11254}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 11267, \"to\": 11281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the rugby equivalent of a 90-yard punt return after the final horn sounded.\", \"from\": 11283, \"to\": 11365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rugby equivalent\", \"from\": 11290, \"to\": 11310}, {\"ngram\": \"a 90-yard punt return\", \"from\": 11314, \"to\": 11335}, {\"ngram\": \"the final horn\", \"from\": 11342, \"to\": 11356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it happened at the end of a very tense game, which happened to be the second game of the day and the third straight day of doubleheaders.\", \"from\": 11366, \"to\": 11507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 11385, \"to\": 11392}, {\"ngram\": \"a very tense game\", \"from\": 11396, \"to\": 11413}, {\"ngram\": \"the second game\", \"from\": 11436, \"to\": 11451}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 11455, \"to\": 11462}, {\"ngram\": \"the third straight day\", \"from\": 11467, \"to\": 11489}, {\"ngram\": \"doubleheaders\", \"from\": 11493, \"to\": 11506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rugby sevens tournament is quick and fun.\", \"from\": 11509, \"to\": 11554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rugby\", \"from\": 11509, \"to\": 11518}, {\"ngram\": \"tournament\", \"from\": 11526, \"to\": 11536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans have taken a liking to it since it became an Olympic sport in 2016, but the U.S. had not really had a signature moment, nor a medal to show for its efforts.\", \"from\": 11555, \"to\": 11716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 11555, \"to\": 11559}, {\"ngram\": \"a liking\", \"from\": 11571, \"to\": 11579}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 11602, \"to\": 11618}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 11632, \"to\": 11640}, {\"ngram\": \"a signature moment\", \"from\": 11660, \"to\": 11678}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 11684, \"to\": 11691}, {\"ngram\": \"its efforts\", \"from\": 11704, \"to\": 11715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now the U.S. has a bronze medal, and it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll be fun to see how much that helps generate interest in the sport.\", \"from\": 11717, \"to\": 11827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 11721, \"to\": 11729}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 11734, \"to\": 11748}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 11754, \"to\": 11761}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 11805, \"to\": 11813}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 11817, \"to\": 11826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m never quite sure how much attention to pay basketball in the lead-up to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 11829, \"to\": 11920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 11829, \"to\": 11834}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 11878, \"to\": 11888}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 11892, \"to\": 11903}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 11907, \"to\": 11919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I usually prefer to devote my attention to sports such as swimming, track and field, and gymnastics, which get a significantly bigger spotlight every four years than they otherwise receive.\", \"from\": 11921, \"to\": 12110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my attention\", \"from\": 11948, \"to\": 11960}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 11964, \"to\": 11970}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 11979, \"to\": 11987}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 11989, \"to\": 11994}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 11999, \"to\": 12004}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 12010, \"to\": 12020}, {\"ngram\": \"a significantly bigger spotlight\", \"from\": 12032, \"to\": 12064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But basketball seems to garner an outsized share of attention just because, well, everyone loves basketball and the players are so famous.\", \"from\": 12111, \"to\": 12249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 12115, \"to\": 12125}, {\"ngram\": \"an outsized share\", \"from\": 12142, \"to\": 12159}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 12163, \"to\": 12172}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 12193, \"to\": 12201}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 12208, \"to\": 12218}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 12223, \"to\": 12234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we scrutinize roster decisions and watch tune-up games and repost little moments when other Olympians geek out about meeting the players at the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 12250, \"to\": 12414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"roster decisions\", \"from\": 12267, \"to\": 12283}, {\"ngram\": \"tune-up games\", \"from\": 12294, \"to\": 12307}, {\"ngram\": \"little moments\", \"from\": 12319, \"to\": 12333}, {\"ngram\": \"other Olympians\", \"from\": 12339, \"to\": 12354}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 12378, \"to\": 12389}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 12393, \"to\": 12413}]}, {\"sen